\section{Conclusion}

AutoMind AI demonstrates a complete end-to-end Generative AI + ML system for industrial predictive maintenance.

The project integrates:

\begin{itemize}
    \item High-accuracy supervised ML model
    \item Agentic LLM recommendation engine
    \item Production-ready interactive dashboard
\end{itemize}

The system is deployable locally and on Streamlit Cloud and is designed for future extension with real-time data and advanced AI workflows.

